{"tid":1222880,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"2019倚天屠龍記 (184) 星期日見!!!","createTime":"2019-06-14T14:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:35:21.000Z","uid":63859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"318abd7adcb4900198e40df475e1161ae5795d54","tid":1222880,"uid":63859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"無忌弟弟身份生死局落場list<br />\n絲<br />\n1.琪言也倩、( 課VIP支持YUKEE+日日簽到張狗超話)<br />\n2.奧邁古陎 (唔係嘅話我星期日遊行個陣大聲叫明教口號出嚟)<br />\n3.2次元黑洞(捐三舊俾保護遺棄動物協會)<br />\n4.大淫賊（輸：捐2舊出去）<br />\n5.上倩若水 （ 每月HKD 150 比無國界醫生）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛香港</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meZezjF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeZezjF.png&h=30c377ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCeqFZG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCeqFZG.png&h=00050a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主演：曾舜晞、陳鈺琪（趙敏）、祝緒丹（周芷若）、許雅婷（小昭）、曹曦月（蛛兒）、張超人、周海媚、黑子、陶珞依、鄔靖靖、安澤豪、傅雋、師小紅、賀剛<br />\n導演：蔣家駿<br />\n<br />\n時代背景為元朝末年，《神鵰俠侶》結尾的近百年後。故事圍繞兩樣兵器屠龍刀和倚天劍。<br />\n小說前兩章延續《神鵰俠侶》的結尾，描述南宋末年郭襄、張君寶的經歷以及武當派的起源。<br />\n<br />\nTVB 預告：<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/9l5quQ5FAYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9l5quQ5FAYM&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=e14a0ff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9l5quQ5FAYM</a><br />\n <br />\n原版預告：<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/CygdCqGSwHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCygdCqGSwHU&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=dfcd59a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CygdCqGSwHU</a><br />\n <br />\n原版第一個post：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1032568/page/1\" target=\"